{"tid":420340,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌...我男朋友食放題竟然無卜位...仲發我脾氣","createTime":"2017-10-01T10:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T15:20:49.000Z","uid":68626,"like":4,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"deb13c8570e0da22b33d7f8b30222ba48ea294db","tid":420340,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左幾年..本身感情都幾好<br />\n佢都幾有主見<br />\n之後我地約左今日食放題...<br />\n跟住佢話有個5點答9既booking<br />\n我地就約左4點3出黎啦..<br />\n但係我有少少野做4點9先出左黎<br />\n去到之後佢話其實佢無卜位<br />\n因為覺得walkin會有位...同埋覺得如果咩都係意料之內就太無聊<br />\n點知去到話要等..我已經勁肚餓<br />\n我就起勢咁屌佢無卜位..之後佢一路都唔出聲咁<br />\n點知屌多兩句，佢話唔係我遲到洗西等咩..<br />\n我即刻勁無奈，明明係佢自己無卜位在先<br />\n之後等位...佢話根據佢估計好快有..點知去到5點55分先有位..足足遲左十分鐘<br />\n佢話預左有...唔知我屌乜...<br />\n但係我覺得佢係到結果論好撚on9囉"},{"pid":"4c38d3a2f836dba8787d1b1c17c9e7f995d5d8bd","tid":420340,"uid":45644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食第二間咪唔洗嗌交囉&hellip;雖然冇book位係衰仔啲"},{"pid":"0b36ddac5300a6388a57762a553d18dfeae624b0","tid":420340,"uid":39482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"起勢咁屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6377a0f47585ebdc77e64f7501cd404e1dded5fc","tid":420340,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"絲打 撐你牙"},{"pid":"3e6ebe2840d33ff81216c24da23a8a75095c4421","tid":420340,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食第二間咪唔洗嗌交囉&hellip;雖然冇book位係衰仔啲</blockquote><br />\n第二間都無<br />\n屌佢真係好撚on9<br />\n無book位仲好意思講野"},{"pid":"449e1038395d5d6b9b3986ad96c36b33a60a7a7b","tid":420340,"uid":139294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:16:06.000Z","msg":"十分鍾都要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm